Package: crossingprobability
Title: Caclulate the Crossing Probability for Poisson Processes
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
          c(person("Lukas", "Klein", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "lukas.klein@h-da.de"), 
             person("Amit", "Moscovich", role = c("aut"),
             email = "moscovich@gmail.com"))
Description: Fast, efficient numeric calculation of the crossing probability
            between one or two boundaries for a Poisson Process implemented in
            C++ with different algorithms available.
